ity"},{"d":"सान्त्वंवा:","m":"Sama (conciliation) or"},{"d":"भेदंवा:","m":"or by bedha (dissension)"},{"d":"समतिक्रम्य:","m":"leaving these"},{"d":"अर्थेषु:","m":"means"},{"d":"दण्डेन:","m":"by d and a (force )"},{"d":"सिद्धिम्","m":"success"},{"d":"रोचये:","m":"attained."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"इहप्राप्तान्वयंसर्वान् शत्रूंस्तवमहाबल: ।वशेशस्त्रप्रतापेनकरिष्यामोनसंशयः","trans":"\"O Ravana of extraordinary strength We will bring all your enemies under control on their arrival here. There is no doubt.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबल:","m":"powerful one"},{"d":"वयम्","m":"we"},{"d":"इह:","m":"here"},{"d":"प्राप्तान्","m":"on arriving"},{"d":"तम:","m":"him"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"शत्रून्","m":"enemies"},{"d":"शस्त्रप्रतापेन:","m":"by the strength of arms"},{"d":"वशे:","m":"bring under your control"},{"d":"करिष्यामः","m":"will do"},{"d":"संशयः","m":"doubt"},{"d":"न:","m":"not."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"एवमुक्तस्तदाराजामहापार्श्वेनरावणः ।तस्यसम्पूजयन्वाक्यमिदंवचनमब्रवीत्","trans":"Ravana, the king of Rakshasas feeling happy about the statement of Mahaparsva, spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"तदा:","m":"then"},{"d":"महापार्श्वेन:","m":"by Mahaparsva"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"राजा:","m":"king"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"statement"},{"d":"सम्पूजयन्","m":"feeling happy"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"महापार्श्वनिबोधत्वंरहस्यंकिञ्चिदात्मन: ।चिरवृत्तंतदाख्यास्येयदवाप्तंपुरामया","trans":"\"O Mahaparsva I have certain secret that happened in the past. It was a long time ago and I shall tell you. Listen to it.\"","words":[{"d":"महापार्श्व:","m":"O Mahaparsva"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"I myself"},{"d":"किञ्चित्","m":"certain"},{"d":"रहस्यम्","m":"secret"},{"d":"निबोध:","m":"listen to"},{"d":"पुरा:","m":"earlier"},{"d":"मया:","m":"by me"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"अवाप्तम्","m":"happened"},{"d":"चिरवृत्तम्","m":"long time ago"},{"d":